title: My Family Season 3
description:
Episode 1: Absent Vixen, Cheeky Monkey

Janey goes to university in Manchester, and an all out battle ensues over her room.

Episode 2: Shrink Rap

Ben and Susan attend an auction at Michael&#039;s school, where they successfully bid on a couple&#039;s therapy session. Meanwhile, Ben tries to avoid a former patient.

Episode 3: Desperately Squeaking Susan

Ben&#039;s cousin&#039;s daughter Abi is invited to dinner. Nick becomes a magician.

Episode 4: Of Mice and Ben

Abi wants to make a documentary of a "normal married couple", and there&#039;s a rat in the walls.

Episode 5: Imperfect Strangers

Janey calls home from university in crisis. Ben and Susan have a romantic adventure.

Episode 6: The Second Greatest Story Ever Told

The Harpers experience competitive family strife over an amateur nativity play. Michael has girl difficulties. Ben has a toothache.

Episode 7: Waiting to Inhale

Michael is invited into a girl&#039;s room. Ben and Susan find a joint.

Episode 8: Misery

Susan visits Janey at University. Michael wants to go to Greece. Nick has a new job.

Episode 9: Auto Erotica

Susan wants to go away for her and Ben&#039;s wedding anniversary. Nick wins a car in a poker game. Michael finds some underwear.

Episode 10: A Handful of Dust

It&#039;s Ben&#039;s birthday, and Janey comes for a visit with a friend.

Episode 11: The Lost Weekend

Michael is off for a higher maths fun weekend, and with everyone else gone Ben and Susan have the weekend alone.

Episode 12: Ghosts

The house may be haunted. Nick opens a mini-cab business. An old flame of Susan&#039;s looks her up.

Episode 13: One Flew Out of the Cuckoo&#039;s Nest

Nick and Ben reach a turning point. Michael tries to buff up.

Episode 14: Ding Dong Merrily...

It&#039;s Christmas at the Harpers, Janey comes home with a gift for the holidays, and Nick has an idea for a holiday business.


I&#039;m in a good mood so here&#039;s season 3 , hope you like it.

ENJOY!!!
